Yes.

34:03.207 --> 34:04.500
(Felix clears throat)

34:04.542 --> 34:06.627
Yes, they did, didn't you?

34:06.669 --> 34:08.379
You did, right? Yeah, they did.

34:08.421 --> 34:10.757
Sorry, uh, is that a secret?

34:10.798 --> 34:13.259
I'm so sorry.
Felix, can you just
give us a second?

34:13.301 --> 34:15.386
(laughs)
Me? I--

34:15.428 --> 34:17.638
Yep, yep, you.

34:17.680 --> 34:19.640
You're the only
Felix in the car.

34:19.682 --> 34:22.268
Okay.

34:23.728 --> 34:26.564
(car door closes)
(Max groans)

34:26.606 --> 34:28.691
Sorry about him, he just...

34:28.733 --> 34:31.319
likes to talk
a lot.

34:31.360 --> 34:34.405
It's all good.
Anyway, um...

34:34.447 --> 34:37.033
Look, I know Murphy's
going to prison.

34:37.075 --> 34:40.578
And you're just
my friend's friend.

34:40.620 --> 34:43.247
But don't go down
that road, man.

34:43.289 --> 34:45.833
I'm not going down any road.

34:47.001 --> 34:49.921
Uh-huh.

34:49.962 --> 34:52.840
Look, I know
you guys had a thing.

34:52.882 --> 34:55.551
Uh-huh.
And that's cool.

34:57.220 --> 34:59.013
But we just
get each other.

35:03.101 --> 35:05.269
This is what she does.

35:05.311 --> 35:07.355
She makes you think
you guys have

35:07.396 --> 35:09.690
this special connection
or whatever.

35:09.732 --> 35:12.568
All she does is distract you
while she messes up your life.

35:12.610 --> 35:14.987
Look at me, man.

35:15.029 --> 35:17.073
I know you think
she likes you.

35:17.115 --> 35:19.450
But she's just using you
to get what she wants.

35:21.577 --> 35:23.663
Trust me.

35:31.671 --> 35:33.756
DARNELL:
All right, take care
of yourselves.

35:33.798 --> 35:35.299
I'll, uh, I'll visit you guys.

35:35.341 --> 35:36.551
FELIX:
Yeah, please do.

35:36.592 --> 35:38.344
MURPHY:
Thank you for everything.

35:38.386 --> 35:40.346
DARNELL:
Yo, Trey, wait up.

35:40.388 --> 35:42.515
What's up?

35:42.557 --> 35:45.059
Nothing, I just want to make
sure you're good.

35:45.101 --> 35:47.478
This is, uh...

35:47.520 --> 35:49.772
you know, it's a lot.

35:49.814 --> 35:51.774
Want to grab a bite
to eat or something?

35:51.816 --> 35:53.901
Nah, man.

35:53.943 --> 35:55.778
I'm still pretty exhausted.

35:55.820 --> 35:58.156
Plus I should figure out
what I'm gonna do for work.

35:58.197 --> 36:00.283
All right.

36:02.535 --> 36:04.579
I'll hit you up later.
All right.

36:04.620 --> 36:07.290
Stay blessed.

36:12.962 --> 36:14.964
Beau. Listen.

36:15.006 --> 36:17.091
It's back on.

36:17.133 --> 36:19.927
I'm gonna need you to grab
as much "H" as you can

36:19.969 --> 36:21.679
before the cops get there.

36:21.721 --> 36:23.723
We want to make sure
we give them plenty of space

36:23.764 --> 36:25.349
to get to the stairs.
(entry bell jingles)

36:26.684 --> 36:28.769
Hey, heads up.

36:37.111 --> 36:39.155
Hello, Murphy.

36:41.949 --> 36:44.035
Hi.

36:48.623 --> 36:49.916
Why aren't we
in a safe house?

36:49.957 --> 36:51.375
Look, I'll explain
everything.

36:51.417 --> 36:52.752
Max Parish.

36:54.378 --> 36:56.172
I'm Josh Wallace.

36:56.214 --> 36:57.924
Nice to finally meet you.

37:00.801 --> 37:02.720
Okay, then.

37:02.762 --> 37:04.347
Should we get started?

37:04.388 --> 37:05.848
MURPHY:
Get started?

37:05.890 --> 37:08.351
Just arrest us and go get Jess.

37:08.392 --> 37:10.144
Well, it's not
as simple as that.

37:10.186 --> 37:12.647
The chief didn't go for this, so
we have to improvise a little.

37:12.688 --> 37:14.649
What do you mean "improvise"?

37:14.690 --> 37:18.194
JOSH:
Look, without a warrant,
our options are limited, but...

37:18.236 --> 37:20.238
if you guys go in first
and lead us to Jess,

37:20.279 --> 37:23.241
then... we're well within
our legal bounds.

37:25.117 --> 37:27.119
Okay, I don't--

37:27.161 --> 37:29.330
I don't care, just tell us
what we have to do.

37:29.372 --> 37:30.831
Okay.

37:30.873 --> 37:32.541
Here's how it's gonna go down.

37:32.583 --> 37:35.002
The last thing we want is
to tip Josiah off.

37:35.044 --> 37:37.755
So you have to follow our
instructions to a tee.

37:37.797 --> 37:41.676
When you guys leave here,
get back in your car.

37:41.717 --> 37:44.303
Gene will place a GPS,
so don't get any ideas.

37:44.345 --> 37:47.098
We'll follow you
the whole way to the arcade.

37:57.024 --> 37:59.277
All right, man.
Here we go.

38:04.365 --> 38:07.034
JOSH:
It's a 30-minute trip.

38:07.076 --> 38:09.829
And we'll have eyes on you
the whole time.

38:25.803 --> 38:27.888
(nearby thud)

38:35.771 --> 38:36.731
Wow.

38:36.772 --> 38:38.274
Al, hang on.

38:38.316 --> 38:40.484
I don't even know what to say.

38:40.526 --> 38:41.944
Is this what you do?

38:41.986 --> 38:43.738
You just steal drugs
every night?

38:43.779 --> 38:46.073
No! Listen, the cops are coming
to bust Josiah.

38:46.115 --> 38:47.867
But Trey's gonna use
what I can get to start over.

38:47.908 --> 38:49.327
What?
We can be
at the top.

38:49.368 --> 38:51.412
I'm gonna be
Trey's right-hand man.

38:56.709 --> 38:58.794
Alex, wait!
No.

38:58.836 --> 39:00.421
I don't want anything
to do with this!

39:00.463 --> 39:02.590
Josiah's gonna kill us both
if he finds out!

39:02.631 --> 39:04.592
All right.

39:04.633 --> 39:06.052
Hey, give me your keys.

39:06.093 --> 39:07.762
Mine are inside.

39:07.803 --> 39:09.847
So are mine!

39:09.889 --> 39:12.516
We-we got to get out of here.

39:12.558 --> 39:13.726
The cops are gonna
be here soon.

39:13.768 --> 39:15.353
I'm not going anywhere with you.

39:16.520 --> 39:18.606
Fine.

39:20.816 --> 39:22.943
JOSH:
Now we'll wait until
the last possible second

39:22.985 --> 39:24.779
to sound our sirens.

39:24.820 --> 39:27.031
We don't want to tip off Josiah.

39:27.073 --> 39:29.575
GENE:
With any luck,

39:29.617 --> 39:31.118
he won't know what hit him.

39:31.160 --> 39:35.039
♪ O holy night ♪

39:35.081 --> 39:39.210
♪ The stars are
brightly shining ♪

39:39.251 --> 39:42.380
(line ringing)
♪ It is the night... ♪

39:42.421 --> 39:44.673
Come on.

39:44.715 --> 39:47.009
(phone buzzing)

39:47.051 --> 39:49.345
I have to take
this call.

39:49.387 --> 39:51.722
♪ Long lay the world... ♪

39:51.764 --> 39:53.849
ALEX:
The cops are on their way!
They'll be here any minute!

39:53.891 --> 39:55.559
Any minute?
Do you have any idea how much

39:55.601 --> 39:57.937
